OL,6,FIn a biting response to the
OL,7,Fchancellor's Budget, director the
OL,8,FInstitute for Fiscal Studies Paul
OL,9,FJohnson said: "This was not a Budget
OL,10,Fwhich addressed the real challenges we
OL,11,Fare facing because it was not
OL,12,Ftransparent about what those
OL,13,Fchallenges are.
OL,15,F"Government and opposition are joining
OL,16,Fin a conspiracy of silence in not
OL,17,Facknowledging the scale of the choices
OL,18,Fand trade-offs that will face us after
OL,19,Fthe election", he said.
