OL,12,FThe PM and the chancellor have also
OL,13,Fpromised to scrap National Insurance
OL,14,Faltogether, but this had led to some
OL,15,Fcriticism.
OL,17,F"Everyone in work is paying tax twice,
OL,18,Fonce in income tax and once in
OL,19,FNational Insurance, that's
OL,20,Funneccessarily complicated... but it's
OL,21,Falso unfair", Rishi Sunak said.
