OL,6,FBut Mr Johnson of the IFS said the
OL,7,Fpromise to scrap National Insurance
OL,8,Fwas "not worth the paper it's written
OL,9,Fon", unless the chancellor can explain
OL,10,Fhow it will be paid for.
OL,12,FWhen asked if he was comfortable
OL,13,Fhaving the highest tax burden in 70
OL,14,Fyears, Rishi Sunak said "the country's
OL,15,Fbeen through hopefully once in a
OL,16,Fcentury type events with the pandemic
OL,17,Fand the war in Ukraine, and the
OL,18,Fgovernment stepped in an extraordinary
OL,19,Famount of support".
