OL,6,FAnother think tank, the Resolution
OL,7,FFoundation, said this parliament will
OL,8,Fbe the first "in modern history to se
OL,9,Fa fall in living standards", despite
OL,10,Fthe national insurance cuts.
OL,12,FThey also said the Budget tax giveaway
OL,13,Fhas been funded by "fiscal fiction"
OL,14,Fpublic spending cuts.
OL,16,FJames Smith, research director at the
OL,17,Fthink tank, told a press conference on
OL,18,FThursday that "big cuts to public
OL,19,Fspending" are coming after the general
OL,20,Felection.
