OL,11,FLabour leader Keir Starmer said the
OL,12,F"government give with one hand and
OL,13,Ftake much more with the other", and
OL,14,Fthat there was "#46 billion of
OL,15,Funfunded commitment".
OL,17,FSir Keir said the government had
OL,18,Flearned "absolutely nothing" from Liz
OL,19,FTruss' disastrous mini-budget.
